              margin-top: 2px !important; 
            ">Trump’s liberation tariffs</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/trump-liberation-day-us-duties-imposed-on-other-nations.png" alt="Trump has described Wednesday as “Liberation Day,” when his administration will impose other nations with duties on US goods" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i>Trump has described Wednesday as “Liberation Day,” when his administration will impose other nations with duties on US goods. Credits: AP Photo
            </i></p>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">President Trump has quoted April 2 as “<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-01-04-2025-h1-1-liberation-day?source=website" target="_blank">Liberation Day</a>” and promised to launch his next wave of tariffs on imports. He claims these tariffs will free the US from unfair competition. While most details are undisclosed, here’s what to expect:</p>
          <ol style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top:4px;margin-bottom:5px;">
            <li>25% tariff on all imports from countries that buy oil from Venezuela.
            </li>
            <li style="margin-top:5px;">25% tariff on auto imports with taxes on fully imported cars. 
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">Trump expects to raise $100B in annual revenue from this initiative. Rumor mills say he might extend the tariffs to copper, lumber, pharmaceuticals, and computer chip imports. Since he assumed office, Trump has launched a <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-01-04-2025-h1-2-slew-of-tariffs" target="_blank">slew of tariffs</a> that already impact global trade. Reciprocal tariffs will ensue and might lead to a broader trade war.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
